  "text": "The admission controller pipeline in kubernetes/kubernetes is implemented across 16 core source files in staging/src/k8s.io/apiserver/pkg/admission/:\n\n1. **Interface registration**: `interfaces.go` defines the core `Interface`, `MutationInterface`, and `ValidationInterface` types. `plugins.go` provides the `Plugins` registry with `Register()` for plugin factory registration. `handler.go` provides the base `Handler` struct with operation matching.\n\n2. **Generic admission chain execution**: `chain.go` implements `chainAdmissionHandler` which iterates over a slice of `Interface` handlers, calling `Admit()` on MutationInterface implementors and `Validate()` on ValidationInterface implementors, stopping on first error.\n\n3. **Mutating admission ordering**: `plugin/webhook/mutating/plugin.go` registers the MutatingAdmissionWebhook plugin. `mutating/dispatcher.go` implements serial dispatch with reinvocation support (via `reinvocationcontext.go`). `configuration/mutating_webhook_manager.go` sorts webhook configurations by name for deterministic ordering.\n\n4. **Validating admission webhook call**: `plugin/webhook/validating/plugin.go` registers the ValidatingAdmissionWebhook plugin. `validating/dispatcher.go` implements parallel dispatch of validating webhooks using goroutines. `configuration/validating_webhook_manager.go` manages validating webhook configuration.\n\n5. **Shared infrastructure**: `plugin/webhook/generic/webhook.go` provides the shared `Webhook` base with `Dispatch()` and `ShouldCallHook()`. `generic/interfaces.go` defines the `Dispatcher` and `Source` interfaces. `plugin/webhook/accessors.go` defines `WebhookAccessor`. `plugin/webhook/request/admissionreview.go` handles AdmissionReview request/response construction. `plugin/webhook/errors/statuserror.go` provides error formatting.",
